Text.SourceString: Did we really get married yesterday? Oh my stars, I can't believe it
Text.LocalizedString: Did we really get married yesterday? Oh my stars, I can't believe it

Text.SourceString: I'm officially your wife now...Oh, and a farm princess!//Do I get a crown of flowers or something? Just kidding...or am I?
Text.LocalizedString: I'm officially your wife now...Oh, and a farm princess!//Do I get a crown of flowers or something? Just kidding...or am I?

Text.SourceString: Our first morning as a married couple, and I'm already thinking about what underwater creatures we'd invite for our anniversary. Silly, right?
Text.LocalizedString: Our first morning as a married couple, and I'm already thinking about what underwater creatures we'd invite for our anniversary. Silly, right?

Text.SourceString: I hope every day is as magical as yesterday. Although, maybe with fewer people watching us...just a thought!
Text.LocalizedString: I hope every day is as magical as yesterday. Although, maybe with fewer people watching us...just a thought!

Text.SourceString: Ta-da! I made you something today! I hope you like it, my love!
Text.LocalizedString: Ta-da! I made you something today! I hope you like it, my love!

Text.SourceString: I'm still learning what makes a good land gift. Hope this one doesn't flop...get it? 'Cos I'm part fish. Ha ha!
Text.LocalizedString: I'm still learning what makes a good land gift. Hope this one doesn't flop...get it? 'Cos I'm part fish. Ha ha!

Text.SourceString: Good morning, my darling! I made a little something special for you. Enjoy!
Text.LocalizedString: Good morning, my darling! I made a little something special for you. Enjoy!

Text.SourceString: Rain on land is so delightful! I love the smell of it.
Text.LocalizedString: Rain on land is so delightful! I love the smell of it.

Text.SourceString: I love the sound of rain tapping on the roof. Let's stay indoors today, darling. Just you and me, please?
Text.LocalizedString: I love the sound of rain tapping on the roof. Let's stay indoors today, darling. Just you and me, please?

Text.SourceString: I never realized wind could be this wild on land. We feel it underwater, sure, but it's a gentle sway there.//Here...I don't even know what to say.
Text.LocalizedString: I never realized wind could be this wild on land. We feel it underwater, sure, but it's a gentle sway there.//Here...I don't even know what to say.

Text.SourceString: Storms on land are so dramatic! What's with all that noise? The wind is so strong.
Text.LocalizedString: Storms on land are so dramatic! What's with all that noise? The wind is so strong.

Text.SourceString: Let's stay indoors today, darling. Just you and me, please?
Text.LocalizedString: Let's stay indoors today, darling. Just you and me, please?

Text.SourceString: Let's make snow angels today! Oh! It sounds like such a delightful thing to do in the snow.//<portrait=normal>What do you think, darling?
Text.LocalizedString: Let's make snow angels today! Oh! It sounds like such a delightful thing to do in the snow.//<portrait=normal>What do you think, darling?

Text.SourceString: It's snowing outside! Can we cuddle? I don't want to do anything all day!
Text.LocalizedString: It's snowing outside! Can we cuddle? I don't want to do anything all day!

Text.SourceString: My darling, it's so cold! Hug me!
Text.LocalizedString: My darling, it's so cold! Hug me!

Text.SourceString: Everything's so quiet and peaceful here, it's like a reminder of the kingdom under the sea.
Text.LocalizedString: Everything's so quiet and peaceful here, it's like a reminder of the kingdom under the sea.

Text.SourceString: Working hard, my darling <PlayerName>$Player</>? Can I get you some snacks?
Text.LocalizedString: Working hard, my darling <PlayerName>$Player</>? Can I get you some snacks?

Text.SourceString: I really like it here, my darling. I've always felt that I belong on land...and with you.//It just feels right, being here together.
Text.LocalizedString: I really like it here, my darling. I've always felt that I belong on land...and with you.//It just feels right, being here together.

Text.SourceString: I'm not much for milk, but those chocolate milk drinks?//<portrait=happy>They're absolutely delightful, especially when it's cold out like now.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm not much for milk, but those chocolate milk drinks?//<portrait=happy>They're absolutely delightful, especially when it's cold out like now.

Text.SourceString: I love you, <PlayerName>$Player</>. You always look so dashing. How did I get so lucky?
Text.LocalizedString: I love you, <PlayerName>$Player</>. You always look so dashing. How did I get so lucky?

Text.SourceString: I miss you, darling. Can we spend time together tonight? Maybe we can watch TV or just cuddle?
Text.LocalizedString: I miss you, darling. Can we spend time together tonight? Maybe we can watch TV or just cuddle?

Text.SourceString: Darling, how's your day been?
Text.LocalizedString: Darling, how's your day been?

Text.SourceString: How's the farm today, my love?
Text.LocalizedString: How's the farm today, my love?

Text.SourceString: How are you feeling, darling? Tired? Can I get you anything?
Text.LocalizedString: How are you feeling, darling? Tired? Can I get you anything?

Text.SourceString: I need a hug. I miss you so, so much today.
Text.LocalizedString: I need a hug. I miss you so, so much today.

Text.SourceString: My darling <PlayerName>$Player</>, I command you to kiss me now. A princess does not wait.
Text.LocalizedString: My darling <PlayerName>$Player</>, I command you to kiss me now. A princess does not wait.

Text.SourceString: Hide-and-seek, my love? If you find me, I'll grant you a wish. Any wish!
Text.LocalizedString: Hide-and-seek, my love? If you find me, I'll grant you a wish. Any wish!

Text.SourceString: <PlayerName>$Player</>, let's play a game of 'guess what I'm thinking.' If you win, I owe you a dance under the stars.//Loser makes dinner tonight!
Text.LocalizedString: <PlayerName>$Player</>, let's play a game of 'guess what I'm thinking.' If you win, I owe you a dance under the stars.//Loser makes dinner tonight!

Text.SourceString: Brrr, it's so chilly outside! Can we have a hot cocoa night?
Text.LocalizedString: Brrr, it's so chilly outside! Can we have a hot cocoa night?

Text.SourceString: Look at the frost on the windows, it's like a Winter wonderland! I'd like to take a walk and enjoy it.
Text.LocalizedString: Look at the frost on the windows, it's like a Winter wonderland! I'd like to take a walk and enjoy it.

Text.SourceString: I never knew snow could be this magical.
Text.LocalizedString: I never knew snow could be this magical.

Text.SourceString: I've heard about ice skating. It sounds like dancing on ice! Shall we give it a try?
Text.LocalizedString: I've heard about ice skating. It sounds like dancing on ice! Shall we give it a try?

Text.SourceString: The crisp Winter air is so refreshing.
Text.LocalizedString: The crisp Winter air is so refreshing.

Text.SourceString: Let's have a picnic by the beach today. I'll pack some of our favorite treats!
Text.LocalizedString: Let's have a picnic by the beach today. I'll pack some of our favorite treats!

Text.SourceString: I think I'm getting the hang of this 'sunbathing' thing. It's quite relaxing!
Text.LocalizedString: I think I'm getting the hang of this 'sunbathing' thing. It's quite relaxing!

Text.SourceString: Summer fruits from our farm are just so delicious! We should take some to Mother, she'd love them!
Text.LocalizedString: Summer fruits from our farm are just so delicious! We should take some to Mother, she'd love them!

Text.SourceString: Darling, what do you think about visiting Mother and Father soon? I've been missing them a lot.
Text.LocalizedString: Darling, what do you think about visiting Mother and Father soon? I've been missing them a lot.

Text.SourceString: Wow, Summer heat really does make you sticky, doesn't it?
Text.LocalizedString: Wow, Summer heat really does make you sticky, doesn't it?

Text.SourceString: Is it always this dry in the Summer, or is it just extra toasty this year?
Text.LocalizedString: Is it always this dry in the Summer, or is it just extra toasty this year?

Text.SourceString: The change of seasons on land is so curious. One minute it's freezing, and the next, it's like the whole world is a sunny beach!
Text.LocalizedString: The change of seasons on land is so curious. One minute it's freezing, and the next, it's like the whole world is a sunny beach!

Text.SourceString: Summer evenings are so magical. The stars seem to shine just a bit brighter, don't you agree?
Text.LocalizedString: Summer evenings are so magical. The stars seem to shine just a bit brighter, don't you agree?

Text.SourceString: There's something about today  that just fills my heart with joy. Maybe it's the sunshine, or maybe it's just being with you.
Text.LocalizedString: There's something about today  that just fills my heart with joy. Maybe it's the sunshine, or maybe it's just being with you.

Text.SourceString: I came across the loveliest flower on my morning walk today.
Text.LocalizedString: I came across the loveliest flower on my morning walk today.

Text.SourceString: Summer nights are perfect for stargazing. Maybe we can spot some constellations together?
Text.LocalizedString: Summer nights are perfect for stargazing. Maybe we can spot some constellations together?

Text.SourceString: Everything feels so lively and vibrant right now. My love, let's dance together!
Text.LocalizedString: Everything feels so lively and vibrant right now. My love, let's dance together!

Text.SourceString: I might visit the museum today, to learn more about land dwellers' history. It's fascinating!
Text.LocalizedString: I might visit the museum today, to learn more about land dwellers' history. It's fascinating!

Text.SourceString: Do you want to take a walk by the lake?//<portrait=happy>What do you people say, stretch your legs? Ha ha! It tickles me every time I say it.
Text.LocalizedString: Do you want to take a walk by the lake?//<portrait=happy>What do you people say, stretch your legs? Ha ha! It tickles me every time I say it.

Text.SourceString: The library has such a vast collection of books. I could spend all day there learning about your world.
Text.LocalizedString: The library has such a vast collection of books. I could spend all day there learning about your world.

Text.SourceString: I'm thinking of trying a new recipe for dinner tonight. Any preferences, my darling?
Text.LocalizedString: I'm thinking of trying a new recipe for dinner tonight. Any preferences, my darling?

Text.SourceString: I wonder how different the stars look from the observatory. Shall we find out tonight?
Text.LocalizedString: I wonder how different the stars look from the observatory. Shall we find out tonight?

Text.SourceString: I'm planning to head to town today and just relax at the coffee shop. Maybe I'll bring a book.//<portrait=happy>Can I get you anything while I'm there, darling?
Text.LocalizedString: I'm planning to head to town today and just relax at the coffee shop. Maybe I'll bring a book.//<portrait=happy>Can I get you anything while I'm there, darling?

Text.SourceString: I spoke to Erika the other day. She's just so lovely!//She knows so much about so many people here.
Text.LocalizedString: I spoke to Erika the other day. She's just so lovely!//She knows so much about so many people here.

Text.SourceString: The pet shelter is my favorite spot. They have so many cute cats there!
Text.LocalizedString: The pet shelter is my favorite spot. They have so many cute cats there!

Text.SourceString: Winter air is so refreshing! Hmm!!! My nose is cold.
Text.LocalizedString: Winter air is so refreshing! Hmm!!! My nose is cold.

Text.SourceString: I so appreciate how you always know how to make me smile, even on a gloomy day.
Text.LocalizedString: I so appreciate how you always know how to make me smile, even on a gloomy day.

Text.SourceString: I've just sorted through our mails, and oh, it seems a bit sparse. We need to make more friends, my darling.
Text.LocalizedString: I've just sorted through our mails, and oh, it seems a bit sparse. We need to make more friends, my darling.

Text.SourceString: I'm making herbal tea before bed. Would you like one too?
Text.LocalizedString: I'm making herbal tea before bed. Would you like one too?

Text.SourceString: I'm finally tackling the pantry organization today. Can't put it off any longer!
Text.LocalizedString: I'm finally tackling the pantry organization today. Can't put it off any longer!

Text.SourceString: What movie shall we watch later tonight? Something romantic or perhaps a comedy to lighten the mood?
Text.LocalizedString: What movie shall we watch later tonight? Something romantic or perhaps a comedy to lighten the mood?

Text.SourceString: Darling, do you think we should plant some flowers this Summer?
Text.LocalizedString: Darling, do you think we should plant some flowers this Summer?

Text.SourceString: Should we plant pumpkins this Fall? I've heard it's a tradition among land farmers.//<portrait=happy>Oh, darling. Let's do it! It's going to be so much fun.
Text.LocalizedString: Should we plant pumpkins this Fall? I've heard it's a tradition among land farmers.//<portrait=happy>Oh, darling. Let's do it! It's going to be so much fun.

Text.SourceString: I swam by the royal gardens today. They are as stunning as ever.//The Queen is truly excelling in their upkeep.
Text.LocalizedString: I swam by the royal gardens today. They are as stunning as ever.//The Queen is truly excelling in their upkeep.

Text.SourceString: Spent the afternoon with the palace chefs. They still remember your favorite seaweed dish and promised to make it for us.
Text.LocalizedString: Spent the afternoon with the palace chefs. They still remember your favorite seaweed dish and promised to make it for us.

Text.SourceString: I had a lovely chat with Mother today. She always has such wise advice.
Text.LocalizedString: I had a lovely chat with Mother today. She always has such wise advice.

Text.SourceString: Maharaja Putput and Nagalita were playing the gamelan in the throne room.//<portrait=normal>The melody was exquisite, a pity I couldnâ€™t capture it.
Text.LocalizedString: Maharaja Putput and Nagalita were playing the gamelan in the throne room.//<portrait=normal>The melody was exquisite, a pity I couldnâ€™t capture it.

Text.SourceString: Shall I request Olan to prepare some kebabs for you, darling?
Text.LocalizedString: Shall I request Olan to prepare some kebabs for you, darling?

Text.SourceString: The King inquired about your well-being...it seems he misses you.
Text.LocalizedString: The King inquired about your well-being...it seems he misses you.

Text.SourceString: I must visit Cho Oyu before returning to the farm.//<portrait=happy>Otherwise, Iâ€™ll hear her complaints next time: 'No visit for Cho?' 'Cho sees many, but not this betrayal...'
Text.LocalizedString: I must visit Cho Oyu before returning to the farm.//<portrait=happy>Otherwise, Iâ€™ll hear her complaints next time: 'No visit for Cho?' 'Cho sees many, but not this betrayal...'

Text.SourceString: I plan to stay the night at the palace, darling. Is that alright with you?//Iâ€™ll return to the farm by tomorrow noon.
Text.LocalizedString: I plan to stay the night at the palace, darling. Is that alright with you?//Iâ€™ll return to the farm by tomorrow noon.

Text.SourceString: It's pleasant to be here sometimes, but I do miss our farm.//Somehow, it feels like home to me.
Text.LocalizedString: It's pleasant to be here sometimes, but I do miss our farm.//Somehow, it feels like home to me.

Text.SourceString: Seeing you here brings back many memories from our courting days. Ah, the nostalgia!
Text.LocalizedString: Seeing you here brings back many memories from our courting days. Ah, the nostalgia!

Text.SourceString: Do you recall the first time we met, after the King interrogated you? Ha ha ha!//I took the stamina berry from his chest and gave it to you. Pssst!
Text.LocalizedString: Do you recall the first time we met, after the King interrogated you? Ha ha ha!//I took the stamina berry from his chest and gave it to you. Pssst!

Text.SourceString: Oh, how I miss it down here!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, how I miss it down here!

Text.SourceString: Does Maharaja Putput seem to have gained some weight to you?//<portrait=concerned>I asked Father, but he said no. He appears rounder to me...
Text.LocalizedString: Does Maharaja Putput seem to have gained some weight to you?//<portrait=concerned>I asked Father, but he said no. He appears rounder to me...

Text.SourceString: I need to arrange a meeting with Semeru to plan my next underwater engagement for when I return.
Text.LocalizedString: I need to arrange a meeting with Semeru to plan my next underwater engagement for when I return.

Text.SourceString: I must make the palace chefs promise not to overfeed Maharaja and Nagalita.//They appear to be getting a bit round lately.
Text.LocalizedString: I must make the palace chefs promise not to overfeed Maharaja and Nagalita.//They appear to be getting a bit round lately.

Text.SourceString: Running errands, my dear? Is there anything I can help you with?
Text.LocalizedString: Running errands, my dear? Is there anything I can help you with?

Text.SourceString: My rooms look just as they did before. Iâ€™m grateful to my parents for preserving them.
Text.LocalizedString: My rooms look just as they did before. Iâ€™m grateful to my parents for preserving them.

Text.SourceString: The staff just replaced the seaweed in my bed with newly harvested seaweed! It feels so fresh.
Text.LocalizedString: The staff just replaced the seaweed in my bed with newly harvested seaweed! It feels so fresh.

Text.SourceString: Are you searching for me, my love? Missing me already?
Text.LocalizedString: Are you searching for me, my love? Missing me already?
